# Add, edit, and delete a peripheral

## Add a peripheral

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, select the **Peripherals** tab.
2. Click the **Add** button.
3. Fill in the required user details.
4. Click **Publish** to save and add the peripheral.

## Edit a peripheral

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, go to the **Peripherals** tab.
2. Double-click on the row of the peripheral you want to edit.
3. Make the necessary changes to the peripheral details.
4. Click **Publish** to save your changes.

## Delete a peripheral

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, select the **Peripherals** tab.
2. Double-click on the row of the peripheral you want to delete.
3. Click the **Delete** button in the top-right corner of the screen.
4. In the confirmation popup, click **Confirm** to finalize the deletion.